      "writtenOn": "2026-06-04T08:37:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "probePixelFormat() can throw (via elog) when the video device open/ioctl fails.\nIf we want the service to stay up and only reject that client, catch the exception in newClient() and return RFB_CLIENT_REFUSE.",
      "parentUuid": "184c5ffb_fedfe62d",
      "revId": "8b36b64e3b9d9c25e7f6ca1761dd0a58271c2463",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
